        <p>Wicka uses both health and mana to power her spells. Her mana cannot exceed her health, but replinishes over time. Her health does not replinish on its own.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="30"src="media/gifs/mana_health_bar2.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h2>Enchanted Candles</h1>
        <p>Wicka can melt the candles she touches and assimilate them into her body, healing her of any damage she's sustained.</p>
        <img id="test_gif" width='687' height="387"src="media/gifs/telekinesis_brick_riding2.gif" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="mySlides fade">
        <h2>Wicka's Flame</h1>
        <p>The flame on Wicka's head can be sent out, to illuminate the subject of her attention, locking the camera to that enemy.</p>
